{"title":"Badamees","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"badam-pista-2-in-1","title":"Badam Pista 2 In 1","description":"","brand":"DADUS","offers":[{"title":"500 GRMS","offer_id":45362021007640,"sku":null,"price":960.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"1 KG","offer_id":45362021073176,"sku":null,"price":1920.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/Badamees_2_in_1.jpg?v=1770627330"},{"product_id":"badamees","title":"Badamees","description":"","brand":"DADUS","offers":[{"title":"250 GRMS","offer_id":45362078581016,"sku":null,"price":445.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 GRMS","offer_id":45362078613784,"sku":null,"price":890.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/Badamees.jpg?v=1770627184"},{"product_id":"pista-sticks","title":"Pista Sticks","description":"","brand":"DADUS","offers":[{"title":"250 GRMS","offer_id":45362129436952,"sku":null,"price":520.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 GRMS","offer_id":45362129469720,"sku":null,"price":1040.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/Pista_Badamees.jpg?v=1770634673"},{"product_id":"sugar-free-badamees","title":"Sugarfree Badamees","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDadu's Sugar-Free Badamees delivers the rich, nutty flavour of almonds with zero to negligible sucrose content, vetted by rigorous lab testing. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eSweetened with Stevia, a natural plant-based sweetener, these sweet munchies are ideal for managing blood sugar levels and guilt free indulgence. With fewer calories, they are a great option for those mindful of their diet too. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCrafted with 100% natural ingredients and free from artificial additives, our badamees offer a delicious and healthy treat that perfectly balances taste and health benefits.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eWhat other Sugar Free Sweets does Dadus offer?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDadus offers a variety of sugar-free sweets, including Kaju Katli, Mysore Pak, Golden Coin, Anjeer Dry Fruit Delight, Badamees, and Khajoor Coin, all crafted for a guilt-free indulgence. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eCan people with Diabetes\/Sugar eat Dadus sugar free badamees?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAbsolutely. People with diabetes can enjoy all of Dadu’s sugar-free offerings as they are sweetened with Stevia, suitable for blood sugar management. However, it is advisable for those with Type-1 Diabetes to consult their GP before consumption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVisit Dadu’s near you for a free tasting and gourmet experience. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn Hyderabad, explore our sweets on Swiggy \u0026amp; Zomato for instant delivery. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Dadu's sweets are fresh, vegetarian, and free from preservatives or artificial colours.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"DADUS","offers":[{"title":"250 GRMS","offer_id":45362161254680,"sku":null,"price":505.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"500 GRMS","offer_id":45362161287448,"sku":null,"price":1010.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/2_efc634e0-81dc-471b-a47a-3f49aa8b85c3.png?v=1742311280"},{"product_id":"chocolate-badamees","title":"Chocolate Badamees","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg\u